        <Parent_String>dressing (hide process) [300053945], hide and skin processing [300229483], processes and techniques by material [300053900], processes and techniques by specific type [300053003], Processes and Techniques (hierarchy name) [300053001], Activities Facet [300264090]</Parent_String>
